:英特爾Atom平台指定的最高[[熱設計功率|熱設計功率]]11.8，其中N270處理器為2.5W，945GSE芯片組為6W和82801GBM I/O控制器為3.3W。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ark.intel.com/system.aspx?groupID=36331&configID=27616&chipsetID=36550 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-04-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916182944/http://ark.intel.com/system.aspx?groupID=36331&configID=27616&chipsetID=36550 |archivedate=2008-09-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ark.intel.com/cpu.aspx?groupId=36331 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312064346/http://ark.intel.com/cpu.aspx?groupId=36331 |archivedate=2009-03-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ark.intel.com/chipset.aspx?familyID=35553 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2010-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100308045140/http://ark.intel.com/chipset.aspx?familyID=35553 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ark.intel.com/product.aspx?id=27680 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2011-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626055231/http://ark.intel.com/product.aspx?id=27680 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
:友達光電的液晶面板B089AW01額定的最大功率消耗3W。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gblcd.com/datacenter/au/B089AW01_V0.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2008-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081030063224/http://www.gblcd.com/datacenter/au/B089AW01_V0.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
:典型的讀／寫能耗的SSD運作時約0.3W和空閒時0.01W。不同的硬盤驅動器運作時由1.5W至2.5W，空閒時約0.7w。<ref name=seagatehdd/><ref name=wdhdd/><ref name=hitachihdd/>
:官方評級3電池連續使用約''3小時''，6電池連續使用約''7小時''。優化了的[[Linpus_Linux|Linpus Linux]]的能耗更低。在Windows XP中，3電池連續使用約''2.5小時''。

