== 問題 ==
;風扇噪音
:早期報導說Aspire one有異常的風扇噪音，雖然這可以使用[[軟件|軟件]]減少。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jkontherun.com/2008/10/control-that-ac.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025102725/http://www.jkontherun.com/2008/10/control-that-ac.html |archive-date=2008-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/community/AspireOne#Step%203:%20Tweak%20/%20Fix |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2011-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515134056/https://help.ubuntu.com/community/AspireOne#Step%203:%20Tweak%20/%20Fix |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 	
;缺乏藍牙
:沒有內置[[藍牙|藍牙]]技術，因此一些用戶增加了USB接口的藍牙[[適配器|適配器]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2008/08/14/acer-aspire-one-not-immune-to-tnkgrls-modding-ways-stuffed-wit/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2009-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122081548/http://www.engadget.com/2008/08/14/acer-aspire-one-not-immune-to-tnkgrls-modding-ways-stuffed-wit |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://jkkmobile.blogspot.com/2008/08/how-to-add-internal-bluetooth-to-acer.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2008-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919134705/http://jkkmobile.blogspot.com/2008/08/how-to-add-internal-bluetooth-to-acer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

;緩慢的SSD
:付運的SSD已經被批評為緩慢的速度，尤其是在寫操作和反應，一些用戶用[[CompactFlash|CompactFlash]]取代原有的[[固态硬盘|SSD]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2008/07/23/aspire_one_ssd_replaced/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081222005005/http://www.reghardware.co.uk/2008/07/23/aspire_one_ssd_replaced/ |archive-date=2008-12-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

;升級內存
:與其他設備不同的是，在不將Aspire one解體的情況下是無法裝拆記憶體。512MB型號配置有一個空置的內存插槽，可用於購買額外512 MB或1 GB的RAM，但不兼容2GB的記憶體。記憶體類型是PC2-5300的[[SO-DIMM|SO-DIMM]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jkontherun.com/2008/08/five-things-i-d.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209014944/http://www.jkontherun.com/2008/08/five-things-i-d.html |archive-date=2008-12-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

